<h2>Pricing</h2>
<p>
  Prowl costs <strong>$10/month</strong>, billed through Shopify. Your subscription starts with a <strong>14-day free trial</strong> — all features are fully available during the trial with no limitations.
</p>

<h2>What's included</h2>
<p>Your subscription includes:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Daily automated scans of up to 3 product pages</li>
  <li>AI-powered issue detection and visual confirmation</li>
  <li>Purchase flow testing (Add to Cart verification)</li>
  <li>Email alerts with screenshots and suggested fixes</li>
  <li>Full scan history and issue tracking</li>
  <li>Unlimited manual rescans</li>
</ul>

<h2>Free trial</h2>
<p>
  When you install Prowl, you'll be prompted to approve the $10/month charge through Shopify. Your 14-day trial starts immediately. You won't be charged until the trial ends. If you uninstall before the trial expires, you won't be charged at all.
</p>

<h2>Cancelling your subscription</h2>
<p>
  To cancel, simply uninstall the Prowl app from your Shopify admin (<strong>Settings &rarr; Apps and sales channels &rarr; Prowl &rarr; Uninstall</strong>). Your subscription is managed entirely through Shopify's billing system — there are no separate cancellation steps.
</p>

<h2>What happens when I uninstall?</h2>
<p>
  When you uninstall Prowl:
</p>
<ul>
  <li>Daily scans stop immediately</li>
  <li>No further charges will be made</li>
  <li>Your scan history and issue data may be retained for a limited period</li>
  <li>You can request complete data deletion by emailing <a href="mailto:prowl@lucyapps.com">prowl@lucyapps.com</a></li>
</ul>

<h2>Billing questions</h2>
<p>
  Since billing is handled by Shopify, your charges appear on your regular Shopify invoice. For billing disputes or refund requests, you can contact us at <a href="mailto:prowl@lucyapps.com">prowl@lucyapps.com</a> or reach out to Shopify support directly.
</p>
